commit message: Cleaned up a lot of dead code leftover from DeliciousDroid.
Slight performance improvement in syncing by making database inserts batch operations.
Rewrote date parser.  Testing shows 4x speedup compared to old parser.
Removed leftover code from old parsers.  Also now able to remove dom4j and jaxen libraries, cutting apk size by 2/3.
Changed authentication verification url to posts/update.
Removed some more old code from deliciousdroid.
Set version number, removed old contact sync permissions, fixed bug with tag cursor not being closed.
